divs: Sighting DetailsIt was the same type starlike craft that i saw at smith resevour on july 19 2008. Once again my girlfriend just got home she works nights and i went out on the balcony to look at the moon one last time before it went down and it came from the west. I immediatly called my girlfriend out and we watched it for about 2 and a half minutes then i ran in put my shoes on and chased it on foot for about 3 minutes. As soon as i ran home i jumped on the computer and checked for satilite locations and the closest one was over mexico around mexico city so i know it wasnt a satilite. Im very excited and wont be going back to bed this morning.
